FNB Connect has unveiled its Black Friday deals, which offer customers reduced prices on contracts for a variety of devices. “We are ready to help customers better manage their finances and save through competitive 24-month deals and discounted prices linked to their cellular offering on sought-after smart devices and gadgets,” said FNB Connect Chief Executive Len Pienaar. Deals from FNB Connect include discounted smartphones, laptops, and TVs – as well a product bundles.  All deals are on FNB Connect TopUp contracts that run for 24 months. FNB Connect’s Black Friday deals are as follows: “FNB customers can also earn up to 15% on their FNB Connect spend back in eBucks, plus receive their Free Connect monthly data, voice minutes and SMSs rewards, subject to their FNB transactional account type and qualifying criteria,” said Pienaar.